Name: Laurel Shrimp in Nimbus Reduction
AttributesDescription: Increases ATK of all Resonators in the team by 25% for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: Food that was once a staple of Rinascitan home cooking, but which has since disappeared from the public eye as high demand led to a precipitous drop in the availability of the tasty shrimp used in its preparation. Today, only a few who purchase expensive shrimp from merchants affiliated with the Order are able to recreate this classical dish.
